Package frc.robot

Class AutoSystem

java.lang.Object
frc.robot.AutoSystem
public class AutoSystem extends Object
The AutoSystem implements all the logic to perform auto routines during competition. Auto routines are defined as CSV files (or maybe now JSON files.). These are read duing initialization. The list of auto routines are written to the dashboard so that the drivers can choose which one to use. This is done while the robot is disabled. The selected auto is run by the auto execute state machine. This contains several sub-classes - AutoRoutine and AutoStep. This a copy of the LabVIEW routine from 2025 season.
